review_text: Very nice park, lots of places for the kids to play, highly recommend it

Busy small park for kids at the hill.
Gets very noisy sometimes as area is not large,  but children have enough activities here  to do: 2 types of swings, slides, a few benches for parents etc.
Impressed by exercise equipment for over 55 years.
A very nice and cozy place for families. Nice playground for kids and good exercising equipment for adults.
Seems to be a nice park for 4 to 8 year olds.  Lots of children with parents.
It is a small park but it has everything for kids. It has sport tools for adults also to do exercises.
Pas super tripper, beau parc pour les enfants avec jeux d'eau mais bon le gazon es rough pour la face

(Translated by Google) Very nice little park next to the library and the Saint Laurent sports center a lot of games. My kids really like going there.

(Original)
Très beau petit parc à côté de la bibliothèque et le centre sportis Saint Laurent beaucoup de jeux. Mes enfants aiment beaucoup y aller.

(Translated by Google) Beautiful large trees that provide shade. Outdoor gym for seniors. Water games (Aquaciel) close by. Picnic tables.

(Original)
De beaux grands arbres qui offrent de l'ombre. Gym extérieur pour aînés. Jeux d'eau (Aquaciel) à deux pas. Tables à pique-nique.

(Translated by Google) Very nice facilities, quiet and pleasant.

(Original)
Très belles installations, tranquille et agréable.

(Translated by Google) Beautiful park with two beautiful group of modules for children. Convenient to move before or after a visit to the nearby library.They added a section of modules for seniors, but I have not seen people use it yet.

(Original)
Beau parc avec deux beau groupe de modules pour les enfants. Pratique pour bouger avant ou après une visite à la bibliothèque proche.Ils ont ajouté une section de modules pour aînés, mais je n'ai pas vu de gens l'utiliser encore.
